phrases: Uh-huh, I just scraped my knee a little.
I thought your diet might be unbalanced from eating out too much.
It is fine, just sit down.
I am sorry, I broke the promise.
I will not ever come again.
This is not what you think it is.
Come on, try it on for me.
Why are you so out of it?
You are the one who invited us.
Damn, he is such a handful.
Why am I the only one who has to work in this dim room?
If only Koshiro-san did not take the day off.
If only he did not take the day off.
Do you want me to make you something?
If you keep eating things like this, you will really get sick.
I will go buy it, so write it down for me.
What do you want to eat?
I do not have a rice cooker...
Then you really do not cook at all by yourself?
I was thinking of buying one someday.
You have a frying pan, right?
What on earth am I doing?
Until a moment ago I was so depressed,
but now I am all happy...
What did I leave the house for?
What was the past month for?
He is out shopping right now.
Oh yeah, I left my pass here, when I slept over the other day.
Are you going out with him?
Are you... going out with my brother?
I guess he does not tell you about these things.
Is there something wrong with that?
You should not stare at people like that!
What did Koshiro go to buy?
Oh, are you going to make it, Nanoka-chan?
I might stay for dinner too then.
Koshiro only offers me things he has on hand, so at least sometime...
What is the meaning of this?
Because you are in the way.
I want to spend today with just my brother...
How is it that I am taking this from you,
who is only his younger sister?
I will not lose to anyone over my feelings towards my brother!
Siblings cannot fall in love with each other.
You are not able to see straight because there is too much blood rushing to your head.
You are probably only able to see your brother who is right in front of you.
But, I do not think such things will last very long.
It will hurt when your feelings disappear.
I will think about him for the rest of my life.
There is such a love, where you can think that.
The rest of your life, you say?
You can say it so easily.
That is why you are called a child.
What do you think everyone else will say?
I visit, worried about you and you are out shopping happily.
What the hell are you doing?
Why did you let her into your aparment?
I tried to make her leave by telling her we were going out,
but she chased me out instead.
What were you thinking of doing after this?
Why did not you push her away?
What are you going to do now that you have got her hopes up?
I do not understand what you want to do at all, Koshiro.
I see that Nanoka-chan is also serious.
I am sorry I said that you were the only one doing wrong.
But if that is the case, then it is more important for you to be firm!
Have you thought about the future?
It does not matter to you!
Whether it matters is not the point!
How can I leave someone alone who is about to become knee-deep in misery?!
Do not judge who is miserable and who is not.
I will not ever involve myself in your affairs again.
I am sorry I was so nosy from the beginning.
Even though she seriously faced me like that,
If she really is precious to me,
there is only one thing I can do...
That even if she does things like this for me it is only a nuisance.
It is no use telling her you do not need anything else.
Should we live together somewhere far away?
Someplace where nobody knows us, so we can live as more than siblings?
That is impossible for you, is not it?
I love you way more, brother!
Sorry...But... if you are going out with Chidori-san and you hate me,
I want you to tell me clearly.
Tell her that is exactly right.
if I do that, everything will end.
W-why cannot siblings fall in love with each other?
I do not want to give up!
That is just glossing over the problem.
As long as I have you, I do not need anything else.
It will not be the same anymore.
Are you really okay with that?
If you are fine with it, then I am fine with it too.
I am sorry I fell in love with you.
That goes for the both of us.
Though there are other people we should apologize to.
I will let her stay at my place.
She does not have school tomorrow.
Okay, do not worry about it.
